        "banner_text": "<p class=\"section-banner__text\">Latex breaks down. Seams split. Grip fades. But most of the time?</p>\n<p class=\"section-banner__text\">That’s on the keeper — not the glove.</p>\n<p class=\"section-banner__text\">If you're rinsing once a week and throwing gloves into your bag soaking wet, you're cutting their life in half.</p>\n<p class=\"section-banner__text\">Here’s how to fix that — and why proper care starts with how you play.</p>"
